---
title: Call Center Integration Flow (DirecTV / Inbound IVR)
---
flowchart TD
    CALL([Inbound Call
Customer Dials Support]) --> IVR[IVR / ACD System
Skill-based routing]
    IVR -->|route to AI queue| ZORA_ENTRY[Zora Agent
zora-agent start --preset call-center]
    ZORA_ENTRY --> SANITIZE[PromptDefense.sanitizeInput
src/security/prompt-defense.ts
strip injection patterns]
    SANITIZE --> CAPSULE[IntentCapsuleManager.createCapsule
src/security/intent-capsule.ts
HMAC-SHA256 sign mandate]
    CAPSULE --> AUDIT_START[AuditLogger.log task.start
src/security/audit-logger.ts
SHA-256 chain entry]
    AUDIT_START --> ROUTER[Router.selectProvider
src/orchestrator/router.ts
capability: reasoning+fast]
    ROUTER -->|cost:included cap| CLAUDE[ClaudeProvider
claude-sdk]
    ROUTER -->|cost:free fallback| GEMINI[GeminiProvider
gemini-cli]
    ROUTER -->|local fallback| OLLAMA[OllamaProvider
localhost:11434]
    CLAUDE --> POLICY[PolicyEngine.canUseTool
src/security/policy-engine.ts
per-tool gate]
    GEMINI --> POLICY
    OLLAMA --> POLICY
    POLICY -->|DENIED| AUDIT_DENY[AuditLogger.log policy.deny
reason recorded in chain]
    POLICY -->|ALLOWED| DRIFT[IntentCapsuleManager.checkDrift
goal alignment verification]
    DRIFT -->|drift blocked| ESCALATE
    DRIFT -->|aligned| TOOLS[Tool Execution
CRM lookup / KB search / account query]
    TOOLS --> LEAK[LeakDetector.scan
src/security/leak-detector.ts
redact PII / secrets]
    LEAK --> AUDIT_TOOL[AuditLogger.log tool.call + tool.result]
    AUDIT_TOOL --> RESPONSE[Agent Response
streamed to IVR / agent desktop]
    RESPONSE --> DONE{Resolved?}
    DONE -->|Yes| AUDIT_END[AuditLogger.log task.end
session persisted to sessions/jobId.jsonl]
    DONE -->|No / complex| ESCALATE[Escalate to Human Agent
HandoffBundle generated
src/types.ts HandoffBundle]
    ESCALATE --> HUMAN[Human Agent
receives conversation context]
    AUDIT_END --> SESSION[SessionManager
sessions/jobId.jsonl JSONL]
    SESSION --> SIEM_EXPORT[SIEM Export
audit.jsonl structured events]
    HUMAN --> CRM_UPDATE[CRM Update]
